data.description: Price reduction AND seller offering 10K towards closing with acceptable offer! Situated on 1.77 gorgeous acres with beautiful mature trees, this steel framed, 3 bedroom/3 full bath home has been well cared for.  New garage doors were installed this year, in addition to a new a/c, 2 new toilets, a hot water heater AND a new fridge!  The NEW pool pump is only a few months old!  Septic system was replaced in 2017.  Pride of ownership is evident! Gorgeous high ceilings in living room, cozy home office and dedicated dining room.  The primary suite boasts a huge, spacious closet.  Your family will enjoy the room to spread out-especially with the in ground pool and patio area!  The pool is completely fenced.  The back porch is getting some TLC and will be completed before closing.  Located in the country, you will absolutely love the serene setting!  Hurry because this one won't last long!
